EN: His eyes are too nearsighted to see things far away clearly.

ZH: 近视是由眼球形状的改变引起的。
EN: Nearsightedness is caused by changes in the shape of the eyeball.

ZH: 近视症常常会伴随着头痛的症状。
EN: Nearsightedness often comes with symptoms of headache.

ZH: 医生建议我每天不要用眼太久，以免加重近视。
EN: The doctor advised me not to use my eyes for too long every day to avoid worsening nearsightedness.

ZH: 近视会导致眼睛发生视网膜脱落。
EN: Nearsightedness can lead to retinal detachment.

