EN: Excessive screen time for children is easy to cause nearsightedness.

ZH: 她小时候就开始近视了。
EN: She has been nearsighted since childhood.

ZH: 她考虑做激光近视手术。
EN: She is considering having laser surgery for nearsightedness.

